    <h1>How it works ...</h1>
    <p class="lead">Hey Mentors! This program is designed to take your busy life with all its schedule changes & shifting interests and priorities into account. You can share your time, talents, & skills in truly meaningful & productive ways in just three one-hour mentoring sessions. Read through the <strong><a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XqnUdYL-BXK_djNxe3IiF2Im_OfVkxAkaoOQYGr-8Bc/edit?usp=sharing">Mentor Program Process</a></strong> to see how the program works.</p> 
    <h2>Finding the Right Match</h2>
    <p class="lead">Take a look at the list below with all the wonderful people seeking a great mentor like you! There are a few ways to sort the list to find the right mentee.</p> 
    <h4>Availability by Location, Day, & Time:</h4>
    <p class="lead">Setting up a meeting with a mentee is easy because each mentee has noted the locations and times they are available to meet - just find the listing that matches your availability!</p>  
    <h4>Project Category & Description:</h4>
    <p class="lead">You’ll also see project descriptions each mentee has submitted - sort through to find one that interests you.</p>  
    <h4>Sign Up:</h4>
    <p class="lead">Once you find your new mentee, just click the button to sign up. After you have completed the three sessions, you can sign up again, or take a break and come back later. 
    <p>Keep in mind that you can choose to mentor someone for longer than three session but that is beyond the scope of this program and your are on your own at that point.</p><br> 
